data.description: Looking for a spacious home in the heart of Lafayette near shopping, dining, & more? Look no further than 101 Crooked Stick! Upon entering the home you're greeted with a grand foyer and formal dining room. The living room is spacious and complete with fireplace as the focal point. The kitchen has a ton of cabinet and counter space plus a breakfast nook! The master bedroom is on the first level, is spacious and has eye catching trayed ceiling. The master bathroom has dual vanities, garden tub, standalone shower and spacious walk in closet. You'll also find a convenient half bathroom downstairs. Upstairs, you'll immediately find a bonus flex space- perfect for toy room, game room, or movie spot to hang out with family and friends.  There are three additional great size bedrooms and full bathroom. Outside, you have a covered patio to relax in the evenings or play in the yard with family. Schedule your showings today!
